data.description:
More For Your Money - Below Market Pricing, No HOA, No City Takes MAKE AN OFFER ON THIS MOVE IN READY PROPERTY!!  Beautiful ranch style home on 1.03 acres covered with pecan and peach trees in Forney.  Home now offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths with an unfinished converted garage that could be a separate living space for visitors, parents or older children.  Entire property is  fenced with an automatic gate leading up to a huge 1800 sq ft shop with electric and plumbing. This home is located in a well established neighborhood with no HOA and no city taxes.  The dining room has been converted into a full size bedroom with closet and window.  Additional updates include fresh paint, luxury vinyl plank flooring in primary bedroom and ensuite bath, painted cabinets and more.  Foundation was repaired in 2021 with lifetime transferrable warranty.  Survey in MLS.
